item.title: Get Your Move On in May!
item.description: We are encouraging everyone in Tama County to “Get Their Move on in May” by recording the minutes they moved in a day. Moving can include walking, cycling, playing a sport, or mowing the lawn etc. You can “Get Your Move On” by yourself, or with another person or even a group or family. To make it interesting, we’re going to see how far we can make it around the globe during the month.
